Miscellaneous Orders

No. A-933. No. A-994. Ed. Phillips & Sons Co. et al. v. Novak, Liquor Control Commissioner of Minnesota, et al.; and Griggs, Cooper & Co., Inc., v. Novak, Liquor Control Commissioner of Minnesota, et al.

Sup. Ct. Minn. Applications for stay of enforcement of Minnesota Laws 1973, c. 664, § 2 (Minn. Stat. § 340.114 (1974)), presented to Mr. Justice Blackmun, and by him referred to the Court, denied. The Chief Justice took no part in the consideration or decision of these applications.*

See also note, supra, p. 1001.
